        <briefdescription>
<para>Configure and start the hardware watchdog. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Once started, the watchdog cannot be stopped without a reset on most MCUs. Call <ref refid="syn__port__wdt_8h_1a0e7f9466b41b8fdc50fe06e4e61ecbf4" kindref="member">syn_port_wdt_feed()</ref> regularly within the timeout window.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>timeout_ms</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Desired watchdog timeout in milliseconds. The port will round to the nearest supported value. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>SYN_OK on success, SYN_ERROR if the WDT cannot be started. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
